10
00:01:59,950 --> 00:02:00,800
Did you regret this?

11
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:04,440
I used to think that I was omnipotent.

12
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,760
But now

13
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:08,830
