14
00:02:09,160 --> 00:02:10,600
You're not that bad.

15
00:02:10,830 --> 00:02:12,880
What's the point of living then?

16
00:02:14,030 --> 00:02:16,390
You're alive. And that matters.

17
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,000
Congratulations, Mr. Feng.

18
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:28,830
There's one last step

19
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:30,160
before we can reach

20
00:02:30,720 --> 00:02:31,750
our cooperation.

21
00:02:32,670 --> 00:02:34,880
Yeah, today,

22
00:02:35,550 --> 00:02:37,830
will you fulfill your commitment?

23
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:48,320
This is a present for you two.

24
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,080
After the wedding is over,

25
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:52,030
we can sign the contract.

26
00:02:52,720 --> 00:02:53,630
Our opium

27
00:02:54,470 --> 00:02:56,800
will be transported into China endlessly.

28
00:02:57,390 --> 00:02:58,190
What do you say?

29
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:00,630
Mr. Matsuyama,

30
00:03:01,830 --> 00:03:02,720
thank you.

31
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:07,550
You're gonna witness

32
00:03:08,190 --> 00:03:09,960
a wedding you've never seen.

33
00:03:16,440 --> 00:03:18,830
I'm looking forward to it.

34
00:03:33,630 --> 00:03:34,550
Miss Li,

35
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:37,470
do you take Mr. Feng Guanyu
as your legal husband?

36
00:03:37,910 --> 00:03:39,800
For richer for poorer,

37
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:42,440
in sickness and in health,

38
00:03:43,190 --> 00:03:44,910
you'll always be with him

39
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:46,910
until death do you apart.

40
00:03:47,110 --> 00:03:47,910
I do.

41
00:03:48,880 --> 00:03:49,960
Miss Feng,

42
00:03:50,440 --> 00:03:51,520
do you want to

43
00:03:51,830 --> 00:03:53,470
fight with me

44
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:55,080
out of the encirclement?

45
00:03:56,390 --> 00:03:57,270
I do.

46
00:04:00,390 --> 00:04:01,520
So do I.

47
00:04:12,910 --> 00:04:13,910
Take the body away.

48
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,270
After the wedding,

49
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:16,640
return it to Feng Guanyu.

50
00:04:27,320 --> 00:04:29,320
There is a towel over there.
Go fetch it for me.

51
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:32,550
OK, you're the young master.

52
00:04:37,550 --> 00:04:38,880
(Feng Guanyu is such a fool.)

53
00:04:39,160 --> 00:04:41,790
(I must step out at this moment.)

54
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:55,510
Weijie.

55
00:04:56,510 --> 00:04:59,160
Huang Weijie. Weijie.

56
00:04:59,550 --> 00:05:03,350
Remember to get me the cure
before 12 o'clock.

57
00:05:04,790 --> 00:05:05,880
Li Taotao has it.

58
00:05:07,350 --> 00:05:08,440
