78
00:07:38,830 --> 00:07:40,040
Let me have a quiet moment.

79
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:50,760
Don't sleep. Hang in there.

80
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:53,950
Feng Guanyu, wake up.

81
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:57,600
Feng Guanyu! Feng Guanyu!

82
